{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"692","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"上市櫃4月營收2.69兆 今年新高","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>工商時報 王淑以<span lang='EN-US'> 2020.05.12</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/4%E6%9C%88%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B61.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 400px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>上市櫃公司<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月合併營收<span lang='EN-US'>2.69</span>兆元，創今年以來單月新高。圖<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>本報資料照片</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>新冠肺炎疫情及油價衝擊上半年經濟活動，在企業提前下單挹注及因疫情、油價干擾的多空抵銷下，上市櫃公司<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月合併營收<span lang='EN-US'>2.69</span>兆元，創今年以來單月新高，但有大聯大、聯電、兆豐金等<span lang='EN-US'>82</span>家<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月合併營收創新高，及台塑化、台化、福懋、台灣高鐵等<span lang='EN-US'>127</span>家創新低，營運呈現兩極化。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據統計，<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月合併營收<span lang='EN-US'>2.69</span>兆元，月增<span lang='EN-US'>0.18</span>％，年減<span lang='EN-US'>2.38</span>％；累計前四月合併營收<span lang='EN-US'>10.11</span>兆元，年減<span lang='EN-US'>5.66</span>％。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>今年<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>月初新冠肺炎疫情爆發以來打亂了企業的腳步，<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>月及<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>月中斷的貨源遞延至<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月及<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月拉貨，並為了確保供應鏈貨源充足，強化了拉貨力道，推升上市櫃公司營收成長，其中電子業及<span lang='EN-US'>IC</span>通路商最明顯，如大聯大及豐藝等。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>至於因新冠肺炎受到衝擊的觀光、運輸、餐飲、航空、紡織、娛樂業等持續低迷，如有台灣高鐵、晶華、台南、好樂迪、國賓、漢來美食等<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月合併營收創新低。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>除了新冠肺炎來攪局外，國際油價劇烈重挫也影響了塑化業、油電燃氣、橡膠產業<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月營收創新低，如台塑化、台化、福懋、全國、華豐、南港等。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>第一金投顧董事長陳奕光表示，新冠肺炎及油價幾乎貫穿了今年上半年的經濟活動，受惠及受害的上市櫃公司營運呈現相當兩極化，<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月合併營收共計有<span lang='EN-US'>127</span>家創新低，比<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月的<span lang='EN-US'>63</span>家更擴大，疫情衝擊下民眾緊縮消費支出。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>統一投顧董事長黎方國表示，美國就業市場雖然面臨史上最嚴峻的失業，但隨著新冠肺炎疫情趨於緩和，經濟活動漸漸恢復，初領失業救濟金人數已連續五周下滑，且美國解除封鎖的州數正逐漸增加，未來經濟即將重啟並回穩。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>黎方國強調，疫情僅是今年經濟波動的一個插曲，為了迎接下半年電子業消費旺季及<span lang='EN-US'>5G</span>新商機，企業並未對疫情而有所遲疑，並確保供應鏈貨源充足，而出現提前拉貨的情況，使得今年台股上市櫃公司的公司的電子業<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月營收表現不俗，特別是半導體產業。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據資料統計，<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>月半導體產業營收年增<span lang='EN-US'>20.6</span>％，電子通路產業年增達<span lang='EN-US'>15.9</span>％。衰退幅度最大的前三大類為觀光類年減<span lang='EN-US'>57.5</span>％、油電燃氣類年減<span lang='EN-US'>54.9</span>％、紡織纖維類呈現年減<span lang='EN-US'>34.2</span>％。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://ctee.com.tw/news/stock/266690.html</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-05-12","clk_count":"140"}},"__N_SSG":true}